{"TopicId":178128,"ForumId":55,"TopicTitle":"Craft Switching","CreatedByName":"quitessa","CreatedById":163900,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-09-07T22:45:07Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"quitessa","CreatedById":163900,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-09-07T22:45:07Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp style=\u0022background-color:#ffffff;color:#353c41;font-size:14px;\u0022\u003E\nSo as an alternative to the [ ] craft switching in scene, can we get the option to right click a craft in view and \u0022Switch To\u0022 like in Map View?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp style=\u0022background-color:#ffffff;color:#353c41;font-size:14px;\u0022\u003E\nThe amount of times I\u0027ve had a craft explode because when I was trying to switch from it to another withing the physics range and accidentally switched to one outside of that range...\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Geonovast","CreatedById":179753,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-09-07T22:50:07Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI know there\u0027s a mod out there that does it, but I can\u0027t think of what it is.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI\u0027m with you on better craft switching options.\u00A0 I really think [ ] should switch between active vessels, ignoring all debris.\u00A0 Mod \u002B [ ] should include debris.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nA customizable \u0022switch between\u0022 distance would be cool.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Cavscout74","CreatedById":181783,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-09-07T22:53:16Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223447096\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022178128\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221536360607\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022179753\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Geonovast\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n2 minutes ago, Geonovast said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI really think [ ] should switch between active vessels, ignoring all debris.\u00A0 Mod \u002B [ ] should include debris\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThat is a wonderful idea!!!!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Gargamel","CreatedById":64714,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-09-08T02:56:04Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223447097\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022178128\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221536360796\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022181783\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Cavscout74\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n4 hours ago, Cavscout74 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThat is a wonderful idea!!!!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThat it is...\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"fourfa","CreatedById":151713,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-09-08T05:20:13Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223447096\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022178128\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221536360607\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022179753\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Geonovast\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n6 hours ago, Geonovast said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI know there\u0027s a mod out there that does it, but I can\u0027t think of what it is.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Ciframe allowfullscreen=\u0022\u0022 data-controller=\u0022core.front.core.autosizeiframe\u0022 data-embedcontent=\u0022\u0022 data-embedid=\u0022embed9752770915\u0022 scrolling=\u0022no\u0022 src=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/141180-14-easy-vessel-switch-evs-v18/\u0026amp;do=embed\u0022 style=\u0022height:225px;max-width:502px;\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThis one?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"klgraham1013","CreatedById":105132,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-09-08T15:14:20Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nEasy Vessel Switch should have been stock a long time ago.\u00A0 Who actually enjoys cycling through a ten craft base on Duna?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"quitessa","CreatedById":163900,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-09-13T21:54:57Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOnly 10 craft? Have a look at EJ_SA\u0027s bases, often upwards of 30\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"klgraham1013","CreatedById":105132,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-09-14T11:55:28Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223450763\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022178128\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221536875697\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022163900\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022quitessa\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n14 hours ago, quitessa said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOnly 10 craft? Have a look at EJ_SA\u0027s bases, often upwards of 30\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYeah.\u00A0 That\u0027s actually what I was thinking of.\u00A0 Watching him cycle through craft is painful.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Sharpy","CreatedById":145504,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-09-26T12:23:10Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nGoddamn agreed Easy Vessel Switch and Easy Board should have been integrated ages ago.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nEVS provides quick switching by alt-click, and quick targetting by double-click on target. Easy Board makes \u0027F to grab\u0027 and \u0027B to board\u0027 act as toggles, so after activating, as soon as you\u0027re in range of a ladder or a hatch you use them.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe two mods I consider absolutely essential.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}